<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2914] explicit dependency to Lua5.2 fails on some systems</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2914</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are some references to  both header files and libs in the lua makefile, which explicitly require 5.2 files. However, even with 5.2 installed this does not work in all cases. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Removing the 5.2 reference works without problems (at least for me).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;openSUSE 13.2, Lua 5.2.3&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
